now how can we begin to understand that when you're in a good meditative situation within yourself and you've become the observer and you're observing emotions okay and you're observing thoughts and you're observing feelings in the body and when everything drops to a calmness and you can still feel these things as objects okay ask yourself what's the mood of the observer what's the mood of the observer

